    ],
    "ron_burgundy_voice": "Well, it appears we have a rather... *delicate* exchange happening at the pickleball net. It's less of a 'smash' and more of a 'gentle nudge,' wouldn't you say? These players are certainly demonstrating a remarkable commitment to not hitting the ball out of bounds. Truly, a masterclass in restraint.",
    "chuck_norris_voice": "Ironvarr doesn't play pickleball; pickleball plays Ironvarr. He doesn't make errors; errors make themselves.",
